pac-ext
-------

Small collection of experimental cli tools for the
[pac](https://github.com/soveran/pac) library.

==  pac-ls
    
Lists all the libraries in packages in a name, 7-char
shasum format, e.g.

    resp 31bf5e0
    ohm  f122eed

== pac-show

A helper utility used by pac-ls to display each line
of packages.

== pac-add    

Adds a line in packages given a name and url and pre-calculates
the shasum for you.

Of course the onus is on the developer to verify that the URL
is trustworthy.

Example:

    pac-add ohm https://raw.github.com/amakawa/ohm/0.0.1/ohm.lua

